quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  18,1,"Ishimwe n’ikuzo byuzuye ni ibya Allah, We wahishuriye umugaragu we (Muhamadi) igitabo (Qur’an), hanyuma ntiyagishyiramo amayobera (ayo ari yo yose)"
  18,2,"(Yakigize igitabo) kigororotse kugira ngo kiburire (abahakanyi) ibihano bikomeye bituruka kuri We (Allah), ndetse no kugira ngo gihe inkuru nziza abemeramana; ba bandi bakora ibikorwa byiza, ko bazagororerwa ibihembo byiza (Ijuru)"
  18,3,Bazabamo ubuziraherezo
  18,4,No kugira ngo kiburire ba bandi bavuga ko Allah agira umwana
  18,5,"Baba bo ndetse n’abakurambere babo, nta bumenyi babifitiye. Ni ijambo rihambaye risohoka mu minwa yabo (ko Allah afite umwana)! Ibyo bavuga ni ibinyoma"
  18,6,"(Yewe Muhamadi) ushobora kuzicwa n’agahinda ku bwo gutera umugongo kwabo (bitandukanya nawe), kuko batemera iby’iyi nkuru (Qur’an)"
  18,7,"Mu by’ukuri ibiri ku isi twabigize umutako wayo kugira ngo (abantu) tubagerageze, maze tugaragaze abarusha abandi gukora ibikorwa byiza"
  18,8,Kandi mu by’ukuri ibiyiriho (isi) tuzabigira imbuga nsa
  18,9,Ese ukeka ko abantu bo mu buvumo n’urubaho rwanditsweho (amazina yabo) byari igitangaza mu bigize ibimenyetso byacu
  18,10,"Ibuka ubwo abasore bahungiraga mu buvumo, bakavuga bati “Nyagasani wacu! Duhundagazeho impuhwe ziguturutseho, unaduhe gutungana mu byo dukora.”"
  18,11,"Maze tubapfuka amatwi (turabasinziriza cyane, baguma) mu buvumo imyaka myinshi"
  18,12,"Hanyuma turabakangura kugira ngo mu matsinda abiri (yagiye impaka ku gihe bamaze mu buvumo), tumenye iryabashije kumenya igihe bamazemo kurusha irindi"